# <type>(<scope>): <imperative subject, ≤72 chars (100 enforced)>
#
# Types:  feat fix refactor chore docs test ci build
# Scopes: {{ commit_scopes }}
#
# Examples:
#   feat(backend): add idempotent migration runner
#   fix(api): reject writes that bypass the canonical state path
#   chore(docker): pin postgres image to a multi-arch tag
#
# Body (optional, only if WHY isn't obvious from subject + diff):
#   - what problem does this solve and what alternatives were considered
#   - any rollback or migration considerations
#   - links to issues, plans, or docs
#
# {{ coauthor_policy }}
